-- Scripts:

local function TWWHYG_fake_script() -- ScrollLabels.AssembleAll 
	local script = Instance.new('LocalScript', ScrollLabels)

	local mainframe = script.Parent.Parent.Parent
	local descriptor = mainframe.Description.Descriptor
	local scroll_labels = script.Parent
	local exec = mainframe.Executor
	local cmdbar = script.Parent.Parent.Parent.CommandBar
	local players = game:GetService("Players")
	local plr = players.LocalPlayer
	local canlagswitch = true
	xpcall(function() return settings():GetService("NetworkSettings") end, function()
		canlagswitch = false
	end)
	
	local switchframebutton = mainframe.Parent.SwitchFrame
	local framevisible = true
	
	switchframebutton.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
		if framevisible == false then
			switchframebutton.BackgroundTransparency = 0
			switchframebutton.TextTransparency = 0
		end
	end)
	switchframebutton.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
		if framevisible == false then
			switchframebutton.BackgroundTransparency = 1
			switchframebutton.TextTransparency = 1
		end
	end)
	
	switchframebutton.MouseButton1Up:Connect(function()
		framevisible = not framevisible
		if framevisible == false then
			mainframe.Position = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0.34, 0)
			switchframebutton.BackgroundTransparency = 1
			switchframebutton.TextTransparency = 1
			switchframebutton.Text = "<"
		else
			mainframe.Position = UDim2.new(0.785, 0, 0.34, 0)
			switchframebutton.Text = ">"
			switchframebutton.BackgroundTransparency = 0
			switchframebutton.TextTransparency = 0
		end
	end)
	
	local TWEENING_BUSY = false
	
	local showdesc = function(reverseProcess, isError)
		if TWEENING_BUSY == true and isError == false then
			return
		end
		TWEENING_BUSY = true
		if isError then
			descriptor.TextTransparency = 1
			descriptor.BackgroundTransparency = 1
			descriptor.Visible = false
			task.wait(.3)
		end
		if reverseProcess then
			for i = 1, 30 do
				descriptor.BackgroundTransparency = i/30
				descriptor.TextTransparency = i/30
				task.wait()
			end
			descriptor.Visible = false
		else
			descriptor.Visible = true
			for i = 1, 30 do
				descriptor.BackgroundTransparency = 1 - i/30
				descriptor.TextTransparency = 1 - i/30
				task.wait()
			end
		end
		TWEENING_BUSY = false
	end
	
	local addcmd = function(name, desc, func, hasArgs, typeOfArg)
		-- creates the label
		
		local total = 0
		for _, obj in pairs(scroll_labels:GetChildren()) do
			if obj:IsA("TextLabel") then
				total += 1
			end
		end
		local lbl = Instance.new("TextLabel", scroll_labels)
		lbl.Name = "Label_" .. name
		lbl.Text = name
		lbl.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 255, 255)
		lbl.BackgroundTransparency = 1.000
		lbl.Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0.075, 0)
		lbl.Position = UDim2.new(0, 0, total*0.075, 0)
		lbl.Font = Enum.Font.SourceSans
		lbl.TextColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(0, 0, 0)
		lbl.TextScaled = true
		lbl.TextSize = 14.000
		lbl.TextWrapped = true
		
		-- handling of description stuff
		
		local insertdesc = function()
			lbl.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
				descriptor.TextTransparency = 1
				descriptor.BackgroundTransparency = 1
				descriptor.Visible = false
				descriptor.Text = ""
			end)
			descriptor.TextTransparency = 0
			descriptor.BackgroundTransparency = 0
			descriptor.Visible = true
		end
		
		-- inserts description for the command
		
		lbl.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
			local stop = false
			local conn = lbl.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
				stop = true
			end)
			task.wait(.2)
			if stop == false then
				conn:Disconnect()
				descriptor.Text = desc
				insertdesc()
			end
		end)
		
		-- loads when the executor is clicked on
		
		exec.MouseButton1Up:Connect(function()
			local text = cmdbar.Text:lower()
			local lname = name:lower()
			if not string.find(text, lname) then return end
			if hasArgs then
				local args = string.sub(text, lname:len()+1, text:len())
				if typeOfArg == "number" then
					print(args)
					args = tonumber(args)				
				end
				func(args)
			else
				func()
			end
		end)
	end
	
	local killbricks_disabled = false
	local damagebricks_destroyed = false

	-- loads healthbrick disablers woohoo

	task.spawn(function()
		workspace.DescendantAdded:Connect(function(ins)
			if ins:IsA("BasePart") and (ins.Name == "DamagePart" or ins.Color == Color3.fromRGB(225, 102, 204)) then
				if damagebricks_destroyed == true then
					ins:Destroy()
				end
			end
			if ins:IsA("BasePart") and (ins.Name == "KillPart" or ins.Color == Color3.fromRGB(255, 89, 89)) then
				ins.CanTouch = not killbricks_disabled
			end
		end)

		for i, ins in pairs(workspace:GetDescendants()) do
			if ins:IsA("BasePart") and (ins.Name == "DamagePart" or ins.Color == Color3.fromRGB(225, 102, 204)) then
				if damagebricks_destroyed == true then
					ins:Destroy()
				end
			end
			if ins:IsA("BasePart") and (ins.Name == "KillPart" or ins.Color == Color3.fromRGB(255, 89, 89)) then
				ins.CanTouch = not killbricks_disabled
			end
		end
	end)

	addcmd("SwitchKillBricks", "Prevents you from dying due to a killbrick", function()
		killbricks_disabled = not killbricks_disabled
	end)
	
	addcmd("SwitchDestroyingDamageBricks", "Prevents you from taking damage from a damagebrick by destroying it", function()
		damagebricks_destroyed = not damagebricks_destroyed
	end)
	
	local walkspeed = 16
	local jumppower = 50
	local overridehumanoidproperties = false
	
	-- walkspeed and jumppower stuff
	
	task.spawn(function()
		local char = plr.Character or plr.CharacterAdded:Wait()
		repeat task.wait() until char:FindFirstChild("Humanoid")
		local hum = char:FindFirstChild("Humanoid")
		hum.UseJumpPower = true
	
		plr.CharacterRemoving:Connect(function()
			char = nil; hum = nil
		end)
		plr.CharacterAdded:Connect(function(c)
			task.wait()
			char = c
			repeat task.wait() until char:FindFirstChild("Humanoid")
			hum = char:FindFirstChild("Humanoid")
			hum.UseJumpPower = true
		end)
	
		while task.wait(1) do
			if char and hum and hum.WalkSpeed and hum.WalkSpeed ~= 0 and not overridehumanoidproperties then
				hum.WalkSpeed = walkspeed
			end
			if char and hum and hum.JumpPower and hum.JumpPower ~= 0 and not overridehumanoidproperties then
				hum.JumpPower = jumppower
			end
		end
	end)
	
	addcmd("SetWalkSpeed", "SetWalkSpeed [walkspeed] - Also makes sure that you don't move when you are brought back to your column", function(new)
		walkspeed = new
	end, true, "number")
	
	addcmd("SetJumpPower", "SetJumpPower [jumpPower]", function(new)
		jumppower = new
	end, true, "number")
	
	addcmd("SwitchOverrideHumanoidProperties", "Overrides WalkSpeed and JumpPower so it is eventually set by default", function()
		overridehumanoidproperties = not overridehumanoidproperties
	end)
	
	local replace = false
	
	addcmd("SwitchAntiDeath", "Used for free defiers and no death runs (at least in the server's end)", function()
		replace = not replace
		local char = plr.Character or plr.CharacterAdded:Wait()
		repeat task.wait() until char:FindFirstChild("Humanoid")
		local hum = char:FindFirstChild("Humanoid")
	
		plr.CharacterRemoving:Connect(function()
			char = nil; hum = nil
		end)
		plr.CharacterAdded:Connect(function(c)
			task.wait()
			char = c
			repeat task.wait() until char:FindFirstChild("Humanoid")
			hum = char:FindFirstChild("Humanoid")
		end)
		if replace == false then
			for i, v in pairs(workspace.Middle:GetChildren()) do
				if v.Name == "Replacer" then v:Destroy() end
			end
		else
			local replacement_water = Instance.new("Part", workspace.Middle)
			replacement_water.Transparency = 1
			replacement_water.Name = "Replacer"
			replacement_water.Shape = Enum.PartType.Cylinder
			replacement_water.Anchored = true
			replacement_water.Size = Vector3.new(1, 250, 250)
			replacement_water.CFrame = workspace.Middle.CollideableTop.Centre.CFrame
			replacement_water.Position = Vector3.new(663.528, 204, 47.1424)
			replacement_water.Orientation = Vector3.new(0, 0, 90)
	
			local idealpart = nil
	
			workspace.Arena.Stages.ChildAdded:Connect(function(ins)
				if replace == true then
					if ins:IsA("Model") and ins.Name:lower() == plr.Name:lower() then
						repeat
							task.wait(.1)
						until ins:FindFirstChild("Settings")
						idealpart = ins.Settings:WaitForChild("Start")
					end
				end
			end)
	
			workspace.Arena.Stages.ChildRemoved:Connect(function(ins)
				if replace == true then
					if ins:IsA("Model") and ins.Name:lower() == plr.Name:lower() then
						idealpart = nil
					end
				end
			end)
	
			replacement_water.Touched:Connect(function(li)
				local player = players:GetPlayerFromCharacter(li.Parent) if player and player == plr and idealpart ~= nil then
					local s, e = pcall(function()
						local function root()
							if char and char:FindFirstChild("HumanoidRootPart") then
								return char.HumanoidRootPart
							elseif char then
								return char.Torso
							end
						end
						root().Anchored = true
						task.spawn(function()
							pcall(function()
								root().CFrame = idealpart.CFrame
							end)
						end)
						task.wait(.1)
						root().Anchored = false
					end)
					if e then print(e) end
				end
			end)
		end
	end)
	
	local delayready = false
	
	task.spawn(function()
		local added_deb = 0
		local a = function(v)
			task.wait(5)
			v.CanTouch = true
		end
		
		if not workspace:FindFirstChild("Arena") then return end
	
		workspace:FindFirstChild("Arena").Stages.DescendantAdded:Connect(function(ins)
			if delayready == false then return end
			if added_deb == 0 then
				added_deb = 1
				for i, v in pairs(workspace.Middle.TouchParts:GetDescendants()) do
					if v:IsA("BasePart") then
						v.CanTouch = false
						task.spawn(a, v)
					end
				end
				task.wait(3)
				added_deb = 0
			end
		end)
	end)
	
	addcmd("SwitchDelayWin", "Used because the server by default detects how fast you beat the stage. This is used so the server is less likely to detect you", function()
		delayready = not delayready
	end)
	
	addcmd("Rejoin", "Self-explanatory", function()
		game:GetService("TeleportService"):Teleport(game.PlaceId, plr)
	end)
	
	local lagswitched = false
	
	addcmd("SwitchFakeLag", "Allows you to either use this cheat or external cheats to look like you're lagging to other players. Good for skipping hard parts.", function()
		if not canlagswitch then return warn("Cannot lagswitch on this executor") end
		lagswitched = not lagswitched
		if lagswitched == true then
			settings():GetService("NetworkSettings").IncomingReplicationLag = math.huge
		else
			settings():GetService("NetworkSettings").IncomingReplicationLag = 0
		end
	end)
end
coroutine.wrap(TWWHYG_fake_script)()

Func HAQuests()
	Out("Getting Quest.")
	;PingManager(180)
	If GetMapID() <> 248 Then RndTravel(248);,$Travel_Region, $Travel_District, $Travel_Language)
	WaitMapLoading(248)
	MoveTo(-5133.27, -5416.97)
	Local $Zaishen_Combat = GetNearestNPCToCoords(-5033.00,-5391.00)
	Local $Zehnchu = GetNearestNPCToCoords(-5019.00,-5496.00)

	If $ZQWin >= 6 Then
		GoToNPC($Zehnchu)
		For $i=1 To 4

			QuestReward(1102)
			Sleep(67)
			QuestReward(1094)
			Sleep(67)
			QuestReward(1118)
			Sleep(67)
			QuestReward(1110)
			Sleep(67);DANACH KICK
			QuestReward(1116);DANACH KICK
			Sleep(500)
		Next

		$ZQWin = 0
		IniWrite(@ScriptDir &"\HA"&".ini",$LoggedCharName ,"ZQWins",$ZQWin)
		;GUICtrlSetData($WinCount,$ZQWin)
		$travel = GetMapID()
		RndTravel($travel)
		WaitMapLoading($travel)
		MoveTo(-5133.27, -5416.97)
		$Zaishen_Combat = GetNearestNPCToCoords(-5033.00,-5391.00)
		$Zehnchu = GetNearestNPCToCoords(-5019.00,-5496.00)
	EndIf

	GoToNPC($Zaishen_Combat)

	If $BotInitialized = "Setup" And $ZQWin = 0 Then
		AbandonQuest(1102)
		AbandonQuest(1094)
		AbandonQuest(1118)
		AbandonQuest(1110)
		AbandonQuest(1116);DANACH KICK

	EndIf

	For $i = 1 To 4
		AcceptQuest(1102)
		Sleep(67)
		AcceptQuest(1094)
		Sleep(67)
		AcceptQuest(1118)
		Sleep(67)
		AcceptQuest(1110)
		Sleep(67)
		AcceptQuest(1116)
		Sleep(500)
	Next

	

EndFunc

title: toher "vj base npc" command
content:
bases del vj base
base_entity -entidad base
npc_vj_human_base -- tipo humano (usado en el de npc de playermodel)
npc_vj_creature_base --tipo criatura

--todo esto definido para el archivo de "init.lua" del npc
comandos sin definir rol
ENT.Bleeds = false -- Sangra el SNPC?
ENT.MovementType = VJ_MOVETYPE_PHYSICS -- movimiento tipo fsica
ENT.MovementType = VJ_MOVETYPE_AERIAL -- movimiento tipo aerial
ENT.DeathCorpseCollisionType = COLLISION_GROUP_NONE -- Tipo de colisin para el cadver | El men de opciones SNPC slo puede anular este valor si est configurado como COLLISION_GROUP_DEBRIS.

comandos de monstruo o maquina
ENT.VJ_IsHugeMonster = true -- Es un monstruo enorme?
ENT.Immune_Dissolve = true -- Inmune a desintegrarse? | Ejemplo: Bola combine
ENT.Immune_AcidPoisonRadiation = true -- Inmune al cido, el veneno y la radiacin
ENT.Immune_Bullet = true -- Inmune a las balas?
ENT.Immune_Physics = true -- Inmune a ser golpeado por cadveres y objetos?
ENT.ImmuneDamagesTable = {DMG_PHYSGUN} -- Puede establecer Tipos especficos de daos a los que el SNPC sea inmune
ENT.GetDamageFromIsHugeMonster = true -- Debera ser daado sin importar qu por SNPCs que son etiquetados como VJ_IsHugeMonster?
ENT.Tank_GunnerENT = "" -- El SNPC que ser el artillero (El jefe del tanque)
ENT.Tank_AngleDiffuseNumber = 180 -- Se utiliza si la direccin de avance del eje y no es correcta en el modelo
	-- ====== Sight Variables ====== --
ENT.Tank_SeeClose = 1000 -- Si el enemigo est ms cerca que este nmero, entonces muvete arrollndolo o alejndote por el gunner para disparar
ENT.Tank_SeeFar = 6000 -- Si el enemigo es superior a este nmero, entonces muvete hacia l.
ENT.Tank_DistRanOver = 500 -- Si el enemigo est dentro de self.Tank_SeeClose & este nmero y no est alto, entonces atropllalo!
	-- ====== Comandos de movimiento ====== --
ENT.Tank_TurningSpeed = 1.5 -- La velocidad a la que se mueve el chasis durante la marcha
ENT.Tank_DrivingSpeed = 100 -- Velocidad a la que circula el tanque
	-- ====== variables de colision ====== --
	-- Se utiliza cuando aparece el PNJ
ENT.Tank_CollisionBoundSize = 90
ENT.Tank_CollisionBoundUp = 100
ENT.Tank_CollisionBoundDown = -10
	-- ====== Death Variables ====== --
ENT.Tank_DeathSoldierModels = {} -- The corpses it will spawn on death (Example: A soldier) | false = Don't spawn anything
ENT.Tank_DeathSoldierChance = 3 -- Probabilidad de que el soldado aparezca | 1 = siempre
ENT.Tank_DeathDecal = {"Scorch"} -- una mancha se coloca en el suelo cuando muere
	-- ====== Sound Variables ====== --
ENT.Tank_SoundTbl_DrivingEngine = {}
ENT.Tank_SoundTbl_Track = {}
ENT.Tank_SoundTbl_RunOver = {}

ENT.Tank_DefaultSoundTbl_DrivingEngine = {"vj_vehicles/armored/engine_drive1.wav"}
ENT.Tank_DefaultSoundTbl_Track = {"vj_vehicles/armored/tracks1.wav"}
ENT.Tank_DefaultSoundTbl_RunOver = {"vj_gib/bones_snapping1.wav","vj_gib/bones_snapping2.wav","vj_gib/bones_snapping3.wav"}

--comando personalizado al morir

function ENT:CustomOnKilled()
	local pos = self:GetPos()
	local pitch = math.random(95, 105)
	local function deathSound(time, snd)
		timer.Simple(time, function()
			sound.Play(snd, pos, 65, pitch)
		end)
	end
	deathSound(0, "hl1/fvox/beep.wav")
	deathSound(0.25, "hl1/fvox/beep.wav")
	deathSound(0.75, "hl1/fvox/beep.wav")
	deathSound(1.25, "hl1/fvox/beep.wav")
	deathSound(1.7, "hl1/fvox/flatline.wav")
end

import tkinter as tk
from tkinter import *
from random import choice
from datetime import datetime

def load_file(word_questions):
    """
    Loads file and returns it split into lines
    """
    file = open('written_answer_questions.txt','r', encoding = 'utf-8')
    lines = file.read().splitlines()
    file.close()
    return lines

def load_word_questions(word_questions):
    """
    Returns list of questions where question contains:
    question[0]: text of question
    question[1]: correct answer
    This can be used for both written answers and yes/no questions
    """
    questions_file = load_file(word_questions)
    questions = []
    for i in range(0,len(questions_file),2):
        questions.append(questions_file[i:i+2]) 
    return questions

word = load_word_questions('written_answer_questions')

def get_random_question(word):
    """
    Returns random question from questions passed in
    """
    return choice(word)

a = get_random_question(word)
question = a[0]



writing= ("Cosmic Sans MS ", 22)
window = Tk()
window.title("Game for two players")
window.geometry("1000x500")
lab_question = Label(window, text = question , font = writing )
lab_question.pack()
e_input = Entry (window, widt= 30, font=writing,)
e_input.insert(0,"")
e_input.config(state="disabled") # zakazeme pisat hracom dokym jeden z nich nebude vybrany
e_input.pack()

def compare(text1, text2):
    if text1 is None or text2 is None:
        return 0
 
    size = min(len(text1), len(text2))
    count = 0
    i = 0
 
    while i < size:
        if text1[i] == text2[i]:
            count += 1
        i += 1
 
    return count + abs(len(text1)-len(text2))

current_player = 0 
player1_score = 0
player2_score = 0
def onWindowKeyPressed(event): # event obsahuje informacie o 'udalosti' v nasom pripade o stlaceni klavesy
    global current_player
    if event.keysym == "Num_Lock" and current_player == 0:
        current_player = 2
        e_input.config(state="normal") # dovolime hracovi pisat do e_input
        e_input.pack()
        print ("Hra hrac dva")
    elif event.keysym == "Tab" and current_player == 0:
        current_player = 1
        e_input.config(state="normal") # dovolime hracovi pisat do e_input
        e_input.pack()
        print("Hra hrac jedna")
 
def onEntryKeyPressed(event): # event obsahuje informacie o 'udalosti' v nasom pripade o stlaceni klavesy
    global player1_score, player2_score, current_player
    if event.keysym == "Return" and current_player != 0: # event.keysym nam povie aky je symbolicky nazov prave stlacenej klavesy. "Return" je symbolicka hodnota pre klavesu enter
        answer = e_input.get() 
        # change everything to lowercase to make comparions easier
        if answer.lower() == a[1].lower():
            lab_ans_true = Label(window, text = "Odpovedal si spravne." , font= writing)
            lab_ans_true.pack()
            if current_player == 1:
                player1_score += 1
                print("hrac1 ziskal bod")
            elif current_player == 2:
                player2_score += 1
                print("hrac2 ziskal bod")
        else:
            lab_ans_false = Label(window, text="Odpovedal si zle.", font= writing)
            lab_ans_false.pack()
        current_player = 0 # ziadny hrac prave nehra
        e_input.config(state="disabled") # zakazeme pisat do e_input kym nebude zase vybrany nejaky hrac
        e_input.pack()
   
 
 
 
 
e_input.bind("<Key>", onEntryKeyPressed)
window.bind("<Key>", onWindowKeyPressed)
 

    
### main

# Load all files
written_answer_questions = load_word_questions("written_answer_questions.txt")

# Start game time
time_started = datetime.now()


window.mainloop()

TER INLIGTING EN OPTREDE VIR ALLE LEDE VAN SUIDLAND BURGERLIKE BESKERMING. – AANSPREEKLIKHEID KENNISGEWING

Ons skryf hierdie boodskap sodat daar geen misverstand is rakende Suidland Burgerlike Beskerming (en Suidlanders as ‘n geheel) se stand, rakende die konteks van die boodskap nie. Ons as Suid Afrikaanse burgers leef in ons land onderhewig aan wetgewing soos gestipuleer in ons Nasionale-, Provinsiale-, Streeks- en Munisipale wetgewing, standaarde en regulasies. As diesulke Suid Afrikaanse burgers, is ons beplanning en aksies daarop gemik, op die moontlikheid, dat daar ‘n tyd mag kom, wanneer geweld so ‘n vlak kan bereik, dat ons regering ons nie sal kan beskerm nie.  Dat daar nie beheer oor ‘n polisie- of weermag kan wees nie.  In welke geval ons op onsself aangewese sal moet wees om onsself en ons mense veilig te hou en te beskerm. Al ons beplanning en gesprekke is slegs in die konteks, en is daar geen intensie, beplanning of aksie wat enigsins verband hou met ‘n opstand vanaf ons, of enige wyse ‘n beplanning van ‘n oorlog teen die regering en/of enige ander Suid Afrikaanse groep of instansie is nie, slegs ‘n PLAN VAN OORLEWING, sou daar anargie wees. Dus, in lyn met die beplanning, onderhou ons steeds die wette, standaarde en regulasies van ons land, en maak ons onsself nie skuldig aan die oortreding daarvan nie. As bevelgroep van ons Suidland Burgerlike Beskerming, wil ons die volgende absoluut duidelik maak sodat daar geen misverstand kan wees daaroor nie.  Onder geen omstandighede sal onwettigheid of enige aksie wat gekonstrueer mag word as onwettig geduld word nie. As dit aan die lig kom dat enige lid hom of haarself besig hou met enige diesulke aksies of dade, of hom of haarself vereenselwig met enige groep of persone wat diesulke aksies mag navolg, sal ons daardie persoon verwyder uit Suidland Burgerlike Beskerming, en ons die lid dadelik skors as ‘n lid van die Suidland Burgerlike Beskerming. Ons as bevelvoerders, kan onder geen omstandighede toelaat dat een of meer van ons lede die ander wetsgehoorsame lede se lewens en omstandighede in gedrang bring as gevolg van diesulkes wat moontlik fokus verloor nie. Onthou ons fokus is om in geval van ‘n wettelose en regeringlose stand te kan oorleef en moontlik ‘n nuwe toekoms vir ons en ons mense te begin, op welke manier dit mag geskied. Ek vertrou dat u die boodskap in die konteks sal verstaan en uself daarmee sal vereenselwig.  Kom ons verseker dat ons dit wat ons doen, gefokus doen, binne die riglyne van die wet.

import tkinter as tk
from tkinter import *
from random import choice
from datetime import datetime

def load_file(abcd_questions):
    """
    Loads file and returns it split into lines
    """
    file = open('abcd_questions.txt','r', encoding = 'utf-8')
    lines = file.read().splitlines()
    file.close()
    return lines

def load_abcd_questions(abcd_questions):
    """
    Returns list of questions where question contains:
    question[0]: text of question
    question[1]: letter of the correct answer
    question[2:6]
    """
    questions_file = load_file(abcd_questions)
    questions = []
    for i in range(0,len(questions_file),6):
        questions.append(questions_file[i:i+6]) 
    return questions

abcd = load_abcd_questions('abcd_questions')

def get_random_question(abcd):
    """
    Returns random question from questions passed in
    """
    return choice(abcd)

a = get_random_question(abcd)
question = a[0]
answers = a [2:6]


writing= ("Cosmic Sans MS ", 22)
window = Tk()
window.title("Game for two players")
window.geometry("1000x500")
lab_question = Label(window, text = question , font = writing )
lab_question.pack()
e_input = Entry (window, widt= 30, font=writing,)
e_input.insert(0,"")
e_input.pack()
lab_answers = Label (window, text = answers , font = writing )
lab_answers.pack()

def onEntryKeyPressed(event): # event obsahuje informacie o 'udalosti' v nasom pripade o stlaceni klavesy
    if event.keysym == "Num_Lock":
        player1=0
        print ("Hra hrac dva ")
    elif event.keysym == "Return": # event.keysym nam povie aky je symbolicky nazov prave stlacenej klavesy. "Return" je symbolicka hodnota pre klavesu enter
           answer = e_input.get() 
       # change everything to lowercase to make comparions easier
           if answer.lower() == a[1].lower():
               lab_ans_true = Label(window, text = "Odpovedal si spravne." , font= writing)
               lab_ans_true.pack()
              
           else:
               lab_ans_false = Label(window, text="Odpovedal si zle.", font= writing)
               lab_ans_false.pack()
    elif event.keysym == "Tab":
        player2=0       
        print("Hra hrac jedna ")
    elif event.keysym == "Return": # event.keysym nam povie aky je symbolicky nazov prave stlacenej klavesy. "Return" je symbolicka hodnota pre klavesu enter
            answer = e_input.get() 
    # change everything to lowercase to make comparions easier
            if answer.lower() == a[1].lower():
                lab_ans_true = Label(window, text = "Odpovedal si spravne." , font= writing)
                lab_ans_true.pack()
                
               
            else:
                lab_ans_false = Label(window, text="Odpovedal si zle.", font= writing)
                lab_ans_false.pack()
   
 



e_input.bind("<Key>", onEntryKeyPressed)



### main

# Load all files
abcd_questions = load_abcd_questions("abcd_questions.txt")




window.mainloop()
